==English==
===Noun===
'''parallelogram of forces''' (''plural'' '''parallelograms of forces''')

#(''mechanics'') a [[parallelogram]], two adjacent sides of which are [[vector]]s having the same [[initial point]] and representing two forces acting simultaneously upon this point, such that the [[resultant]] of the forces is given by the [[diagonal]] of the parallelogram that passes through this point.

